'''[[Agent/Legends|Agent]] Ralls''' was a junior officer of [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]] who was assigned to interrogate [[Davith Sconn]], probably in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]].

The former [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officer was amused by Ralls's naïve innocence, and told him about some of his more colorful experiences in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] in order to shock him. To Sconn's own surprise, this led to a personal interview between him and [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], who was seeking more information about [[N'zoth]].

